## `tests/test_basic.py`

```python
from braille_progress import Progress

def test_construct():
    p = Progress(force_tty=False, force_color=False)  # CI에서도 동작
    h = p.add("t", total=3)
    p.update(h, stage="validated", total=3)
    for _ in range(3):
        h.advance(stage="writing")
    p.done(h)
    assert p.all_finished()
```